        Address: 1028 Manuel Road, Arnold, CA
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Murphys Fire Protection District</strong><br />
        General Inquiries: <a href="tel:+12097283864">(209) 728-3864</a><br />
        Address: 37 Jones Street, Murphys, CA
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Animal Control</h2>
    <p>
      Calaveras County Animal Services handles stray animals, wildlife, and other animal-related
      concerns for the Arnold and Murphys areas.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Calaveras County Animal Services</strong><br />
        General Assistance: <a href="tel:+12097546509">(209) 754-6509</a>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>U.S. Forest Service and Fire Prevention</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>California Department of Forestry and Fire Protection (CAL FIRE)</strong><br />
        For forestry and fire-related concerns, contact through the local fire districts.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Calaveras Ranger District</strong><br />
        General Inquiries: <a href="tel:+12097951381">(209) 795-1381</a>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Poison Control</h2>
    <p>
      The Poison Control Hotline is available nationwide for poison-related emergencies and general
      information.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Poison Control Hotline</strong><br />
        Immediate Assistance: <a href="tel:+18002221222">1-800-222-1222</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </Content>
</Layout>
